        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The scatter plot displays stock trading volume against the next closing price, helping to understand whether higher or lower trading activity is associated with changes in future stock prices.</run>
